            "body": "<div class=\"ex-message-content\" style=\"max-width:600px;\">\n<div style=\"padding-bottom:10px;\">\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">Companies will spend over $670 billion on digital ads this year.</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">Crazy, right?</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">When we chat with Global 1000 brands, they don't have an issue with spending money on paid ads.</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">After all, more spend = more revenue (usually).</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">But here's the shocker:</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">Hardly any of those brands invest even 1% of that in conversion rate optimization (CRO).</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">Why pour $100 million into ads but leave extra conversions untouched on the table?</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\"><strong>It's the biggest missed opportunity we continually see.</strong></p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">Without ongoing CRO, brands leave easy 10-20% revenue lifts just sitting there.</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">Just think about that\u2026 10% lift is 67 billion dollars.</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">And conversion lifts typically turn straight into profits.</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">See, ad costs creep up over time. It's inevitable. Boosting conversions counteracts rising CPAs.</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">That's how you protect and expand margins in the face of rising ad costs.</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">But too many big brands ignore CRO and plow ahead with ever-bigger ad budgets.</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">Don't fall into the same trap.</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">The cost-saving opportunities are waiting... <a href=\"https://click.convertkit-mail.\"><u>reach out to my team to seize them.</u></a>\u200b</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">Cheers,</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">Neil Patel</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">\u200b</p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\"><em>PS: While you're optimizing your pages for maximum conversions, don't forget to optimize your ads for peak performance as well.</em> <a href=\"https://click.convertkit-mail.com/o8uxznovp7cqhk93ql4u2cpdr47rr/n2hohvh36w0k6xb6/aHR0cHM6Ly9hZHNncmFkZXIuY29tLz91dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9Y29udmVydGtpdC1saXN0JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj11cy1ta3QtY2FtcGFpZ25zLW1xbC10b29sLWFkcy1ncmFkZXImdXRtX2NvbnRlbnQ9aW52aXRhdGlvbi1hZHMtZ3JhZGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPWphbi0zMS1lbWFpbC1jay1wcw==\"><em>My Ads Grader tool can help you, and it's free</em></a><em>!</em></p>\n<p class=\"ex-\" style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\">\u200b<br>\n\u200b</p>\n</div>\n<br>\n<br>\n<small><a href=\"https://unsubscribe.convertkit-mail.com/o8uxznovp7cqhk93ql4u2cpdr47rr\">Unsubscribe</a> | <a href=\"https://preferences.convertkit-mail.com/o8uxznovp7cqhk93ql4u2cpdr47rr\">Update your profile</a> | 9710 River Trader St, Las Vegas, Nevada 89178<br></small></div>\n\n<img src=\"https://open.convertkit-mail.com/o8uxznovp7cqhk93ql4u2cpdr47rr\" alt=\"\" />",
